      • endVertices

        Graph.Vertex<V>[] endVertices​(Graph.Edge<E> edge)
        Returns the two end-point vertices of edge e. For a directed graph, the first vertex is the source vertex and the second is the destination vertex
        Parameters:
        edge - the edge being observed
        Returns:
        an array containing the two vertices that connect the edge
